      "content": "i get that but i really cant go to the er right now, it's like 2am and i don't have the money for an urgent care visit. the pain is just making me panic. if i dont take something else, i'm gonna be up all night. isn't there some way to stagger them or just take a bit more so it actually works? i feel like if i just get the dose right i'll be fine.",
